-- Sandy Koufax to be Called as Witness in Mets Owners Madoff Investment Case
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2012-03-13T14:40:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/sandy-koufax-to-be-called-as-witness-in-mets-owners-madoff-investment-case.html
Sandy Koufax , the Hall of Fame
left-handed pitcher for the Los Angeles Dodgers baseball team,
will be called as a witness at the New York trial over whether
the owners of the  New York Mets  should pay $303 million to
investors defrauded by  Bernard Madoff .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bob Van Voris in New York at 
 rvanvoris@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David E. Rovella at 
 drovella@bloomberg.net  